X-Correlation-ID: {{CorrelationId}}

###############################################################################
### NOTES FOR TESTING
###############################################################################
### 
### 1. Replace {{Token}} with actual bearer token before executing requests
### 2. Replace {{CreatedHereditamentId}} with ID from successful create response
### 3. Replace {{TestUprn}} with valid UPRN from existing Hereditament
### 4. Correlation IDs are auto-generated using {{$timestamp}}
### 5. Monitor X-Correlation-ID header in responses for distributed tracing
### 6. Check response headers for any additional metadata
### 7. Validate error messages match expected format from ApiResponse
### 8. Verify pagination metadata in PagedApiResponse results
### 9. Test sequence: Create → Read → Search → Update → Delete → Restore
### 10. Run authentication tests last to ensure other tests pass first
###############################################################################

